  "description": "A calm, welcoming front garden designed to reflect the natural character of the local landscape. Using a palette of indigenous and native species, the design balances structure and softness, providing seasonal variation, subtle colour, and ecological value. Three distinct zones -- entrance garden, scented tunnel pathway, and driveway garden -- create a layered experience from street to home. Through layered foliage, water-wise species, and pollinator-friendly flowering plants, this garden becomes a living habitat, a place of quiet reflection, biodiversity, and beauty viewed from every angle.",
